<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us - Aditi's Fashionista Blog</title>
  <style>
    /* General Styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      padding-top: 20px; /* Add padding to the top */
      padding-right: 20px; /* Add padding to the right */
      box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding in the total width */
    }
    

    .container {
      width: 80%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* About Section Styles */
    .about-section {
      padding: 50px 0;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-section h2 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .about-section p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .profile-picture img {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 5px solid #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: top center; 
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About Fashionista Blog</h2>
    <p>Welcome to Aditi's Fashionista Blog, your ultimate destination for all things fashion! I'm Aditi, and I'm passionate about sharing the latest trends, style tips, and fashion news with you, my dear readers. Whether you're a fashion enthusiast or just looking for some inspiration, you'll find everything you need right here.</p>
    <p>I'm dedicated to bringing you engaging content that will keep you informed and inspired. From runway reviews to celebrity style breakdowns, I cover it all.</p>
    <p>So sit back, relax, and let me take you on a journey through the exciting world of fashion. Stay stylish!</p>
    <div class="profile-picture">
      <img src="/img/blogpic.jpg" alt="Aditi's Profile Picture">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

